translation: Hope you can stick that back on!{#Name="Dito"}
source: Hope you can stick that back on!{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Lady Zero, is your arm all right?{#Name="Decadus"}
source: Lady Zero, is your arm all right?{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: ...It doesn't seem to feel pain anymore.{#Name="Zero"}
source: ...It doesn't seem to feel pain anymore.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Seems I'm getting less human by the day.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Seems I'm getting less human by the day.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Oh, and don't tell Mikhail about this.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Oh, and don't tell Mikhail about this.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Make your way through the underground ruins.{#Name="説明文"}
source: Make your way through the underground ruins.{#Name="説明文"}

translation: How could she have made it all the way here!?{#Name="Soldier A"}
source: How could she have made it all the way here!?{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: Stand tall! She's injured, too!{#Name="Soldier B"}
source: Stand tall! She's injured, too!{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: I...I can't stop the bleeding!{#Name="Soldier D"}
source: I...I can't stop the bleeding!{#Name="Soldier D"}

translation: That's her? I could take her on barehanded!{#Name="Soldier B"}
source: That's her? I could take her on barehanded!{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: Wh-What're you doing!? You'll be killed!{#Name="Soldier G"}
source: Wh-What're you doing!? You'll be killed!{#Name="Soldier G"}

translation: Death is but a door! Do not fear it!{#Name="Soldier E"}
source: Death is but a door! Do not fear it!{#Name="Soldier E"}

translation: Ah... Aaaaaah! I can't! I just can't do this!{#Name="Soldier G"}
source: Ah... Aaaaaah! I can't! I just can't do this!{#Name="Soldier G"}

translation: The eternal sun herself, Lady Two, watches over us! Now fight!{#Name="Soldier F"}
source: The eternal sun herself, Lady Two, watches over us! Now fight!{#Name="Soldier F"}

translation: I heard she was scrawny, but daaaamn!{#Name="Soldier C"}
source: I heard she was scrawny, but daaaamn!{#Name="Soldier C"}

translation: And I heard she was pretty, but daaaaaaaamn!{#Name="Soldier D"}
source: And I heard she was pretty, but daaaaaaaamn!{#Name="Soldier D"}

translation: Well, I heard she'll kill you in your sleep! So shut up and stay alert!{#Name="Soldier E"}
source: Well, I heard she'll kill you in your sleep! So shut up and stay alert!{#Name="Soldier E"}

translation: The darkness is enveloping us all!{#Name="Soldier B"}
source: The darkness is enveloping us all!{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: Wh-What are you talking about? Are you all right?{#Name="Soldier G"}
source: Wh-What are you talking about? Are you all right?{#Name="Soldier G"}

translation: Shit! Is this woman invincible!?{#Name="Soldier F"}
source: Shit! Is this woman invincible!?{#Name="Soldier F"}

translation: Maybe. But we've got to kill her anyway!{#Name="Soldier A"}
source: Maybe. But we've got to kill her anyway!{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: Don't chase her too far in!{#Name="Soldier E"}
source: Don't chase her too far in!{#Name="Soldier E"}

translation: Even if I wanted to, she's too fast to keep up with!{#Name="Soldier C"}
source: Even if I wanted to, she's too fast to keep up with!{#Name="Soldier C"}

translation: We can't... We can't let ourselves be annihilated!{#Name="Soldier A"}
source: We can't... We can't let ourselves be annihilated!{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: Sir! No survivors found in the first squadron!{#Name="Soldier G"}
source: Sir! No survivors found in the first squadron!{#Name="Soldier G"}

translation: Shit. Now what do we do!?{#Name="Soldier A"}
source: Shit. Now what do we do!?{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: This darkness makes it hard to see.{#Name="Decadus"}
source: This darkness makes it hard to see.{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: Oh ho ho! Who needs darkness?{LF}Pretty much anything makes me hard!{#Name="Octa"}
source: Oh ho ho! Who needs darkness?{LF}Pretty much anything makes me hard!{#Name="Octa"}

translation: But that's not even...{LF}You really are hopeless, Octa.{#Name="Dito"}
source: But that's not even...{LF}You really are hopeless, Octa.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Tell me where Two is, or you're dead!{LF}And if you don't know...you're still dead!{#Name="Zero"}
source: Tell me where Two is, or you're dead!{LF}And if you don't know...you're still dead!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Ho ho! Ever the gung-ho Intoner, eh?{#Name="Octa"}
source: Ho ho! Ever the gung-ho Intoner, eh?{#Name="Octa"}

translation: It's too dark for me to aim well...{#Name="Decadus"}
source: It's too dark for me to aim well...{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: Enough excuses, freak. Just keep fighting.{#Name="Dito"}
source: Enough excuses, freak. Just keep fighting.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: All this fighting... We're going{LF}to damage the ruins!{#Name="Decadus"}
source: All this fighting... We're going{LF}to damage the ruins!{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: My lady, these ruins are extremely valuable and—{#Name="Decadus"}
source: My lady, these ruins are extremely valuable and—{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: Ugh, these guys again? I'm getting sick of this.{#Name="Dito"}
source: Ugh, these guys again? I'm getting sick of this.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Come on, Z, let's get this over with!{#Name="Dito"}
source: Come on, Z, let's get this over with!{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Magic drives these beasts.{LF}Yet where does it come from?{#Name="Octa"}
source: Magic drives these beasts.{LF}Yet where does it come from?{#Name="Octa"}

translation: This will require both quick reflexes{LF}and extreme patience.{#Name="Decadus"}
source: This will require both quick reflexes{LF}and extreme patience.{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: I'd rather just break 'em in half and bury 'em{LF}along with this whole damn place.{#Name="Zero"}
source: I'd rather just break 'em in half and bury 'em{LF}along with this whole damn place.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Lady Zero's crude behavior is quite troubling, no?{#Name="Octa"}
source: Lady Zero's crude behavior is quite troubling, no?{#Name="Octa"}

translation: Well... I prefer to think of it as...spontaneous.{#Name="Decadus"}
source: Well... I prefer to think of it as...spontaneous.{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: No, I think "crude" is the better word here.{#Name="Dito"}
source: No, I think "crude" is the better word here.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: I mean, hell, she ate raw meat{LF}off the floor earlier!{#Name="Dito"}
source: I mean, hell, she ate raw meat{LF}off the floor earlier!{#Name="Dito"}

translation: I've seen dogs who are pickier than that.{#Name="Dito"}
source: I've seen dogs who are pickier than that.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: An Intoner who's cruder than a dog?{LF}Oh ho! That pushes all my buttons!{#Name="Octa"}
source: An Intoner who's cruder than a dog?{LF}Oh ho! That pushes all my buttons!{#Name="Octa"}

translation: Shut up before I pull out all your tongues!{#Name="Zero"}
source: Shut up before I pull out all your tongues!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Nice little trick there. Who's this guy?{#Name="Zero"}
source: Nice little trick there. Who's this guy?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Is that different from a sorcerer?{LF}I can't keep track of these assholes.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Is that different from a sorcerer?{LF}I can't keep track of these assholes.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Better be careful, Z.{LF}You don't wanna piss these guys off.{#Name="Dito"}
source: Better be careful, Z.{LF}You don't wanna piss these guys off.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: I mean, they pretty much sold{LF}their souls to gain power.{#Name="Dito"}
source: I mean, they pretty much sold{LF}their souls to gain power.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Yeah? They can sell their assholes{LF}for all I care—they're mine, now!{#Name="Zero"}
source: Yeah? They can sell their assholes{LF}for all I care—they're mine, now!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Oh, come on! We're STILL not done with this?{#Name="Zero"}
source: Oh, come on! We're STILL not done with this?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: My lady, please remain calm.{LF}Anger will solve nothing here.{#Name="Decadus"}
source: My lady, please remain calm.{LF}Anger will solve nothing here.{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: Oh ho ho! Another of Lady Zero's{LF}beloved jumping puzzles, I see.{#Name="Octa"}
source: Oh ho ho! Another of Lady Zero's{LF}beloved jumping puzzles, I see.{#Name="Octa"}

translation: But seriously, what's powering all this?{#Name="Dito"}
source: But seriously, what's powering all this?{#Name="Dito"}

translation: You know how it goes. Weird shit like this{LF}always gets written off as magic.{#Name="Zero"}
source: You know how it goes. Weird shit like this{LF}always gets written off as magic.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Hmm. It appears to be an underground lair...{#Name="Octa"}
source: Hmm. It appears to be an underground lair...{#Name="Octa"}

translation: They built it right into the ruins. How clever.{#Name="Decadus"}
source: They built it right into the ruins. How clever.{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: Pfft! They got a bunch of juniors{LF}guarding this place.{#Name="Dito"}
source: Pfft! They got a bunch of juniors{LF}guarding this place.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Funny to hear you calling anyone "junior."{#Name="Zero"}
source: Funny to hear you calling anyone "junior."{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Hey, cram it! I told you, I'm 22!{#Name="Dito"}
source: Hey, cram it! I told you, I'm 22!{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Stay calm and remember what we taught you!{#Name="Soldier A"}
source: Stay calm and remember what we taught you!{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: It's time to show Lady Two what you've got!{#Name="Soldier B"}
source: It's time to show Lady Two what you've got!{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: This is no training ground any longer!{#Name="Soldier F"}
source: This is no training ground any longer!{#Name="Soldier F"}

translation: This is real, you hear me?{LF}The fighting AND the dying!{#Name="Soldier F"}
source: This is real, you hear me?{LF}The fighting AND the dying!{#Name="Soldier F"}

translation: 戦場だ！戦場になったんだよ！{#Name="兵士"}
source: 戦場だ！戦場になったんだよ！{#Name="兵士"}

translation: You may be new recruits,{LF}but you're still soldiers!{#Name="Soldier G"}
source: You may be new recruits,{LF}but you're still soldiers!{#Name="Soldier G"}

translation: Fight well, and Lady Two may{LF}choose you for her elite guard!{#Name="Soldier G"}
source: Fight well, and Lady Two may{LF}choose you for her elite guard!{#Name="Soldier G"}

translation: Oh ho ho! That's quite the arm Lady Zero has!{#Name="Octa"}
source: Oh ho ho! That's quite the arm Lady Zero has!{#Name="Octa"}

translation: Oh, trust me, it's not just her arm.{LF}Z can actually regrow almost anything.{#Name="Dito"}
source: Oh, trust me, it's not just her arm.{LF}Z can actually regrow almost anything.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Probably grossed out. He's pretty{LF}delicate...for a freak.{#Name="Dito"}
source: Probably grossed out. He's pretty{LF}delicate...for a freak.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: An Intoner with detachable arms too much for you?{#Name="Zero"}
source: An Intoner with detachable arms too much for you?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: No, my lady. As your disciple, I must learn{LF}all there is to know about you.{#Name="Decadus"}
source: No, my lady. As your disciple, I must learn{LF}all there is to know about you.{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: Indeed. There are far more horrific{LF}things in the world, after all.{#Name="Octa"}
source: Indeed. There are far more horrific{LF}things in the world, after all.{#Name="Octa"}

translation: Cent claimed Zero's dragon would be her downfall.{#Name="Accord"}
source: Cent claimed Zero's dragon would be her downfall.{#Name="Accord"}

translation: What was the meaning behind this ominous prophecy?{#Name="Accord"}
source: What was the meaning behind this ominous prophecy?{#Name="Accord"}

translation: In search of information, Zero traveled to the ruins beneath the Land of Sands…{#Name="Accord"}
source: In search of information, Zero traveled to the ruins beneath the Land of Sands…{#Name="Accord"}

translation: Zero's here! Hurry, burn the papers!{#Name="Soldier A"}
source: Zero's here! Hurry, burn the papers!{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: Don't let her reach Lady Two!{#Name="Soldier A"}
source: Don't let her reach Lady Two!{#Name="Soldier A"}
